You now have a fully functional GCP pipeline:

```
[GCS: input.md]
   â†“
[Dataproc: wordcount.py]
   â†“
[GCS output: CSVs]
   â†“
[BigQuery: wordcount_ds.wordcount_result]
```

All triggered and orchestrated via **Cloud Composer (Airflow)**.

